vote.title: Authorize acquisition of a wastewater easement from Northaven/Central Expressway, LTD, of approximately 9,528 square feet of land located near the intersection of North Central Expressway and Park Central Plaza for the White Rock Interceptor US Highway 75 Crossing Project - Not to exceed $260,190.00 ($257,190.00, plus closing costs and title expenses not to exceed $3,000.00) - Financing: Wastewater Construction Fund ($234,000.00) and Wastewater Capital Improvement F Fund ($26,190.00)
